$about_description1.value: Securely store crypto, explore decentralized apps, and make blockchain payments at the **speed of light**.

$about_description2.value: The wallet is **non-custodial and safe**. The developers **do not** have access to your funds, browser history or any other information.

$about_extension_description2.value: TON Magic provides native **Telegram integration** by patching the official Telegram Web app.

$about_extension_description3.value: Turn it on to send and receive Toncoins from any Telegram user.
